      ** Error message data array (<ErrArrMax> x 45A, returned to caller)
     C                   PARM                    MsgDtaXArr
      ** The instrument types format (data strucure)
     C                   PARM                    INTY
 
      ** Inputs to this procedure
      ** ------------------------
      ** Instrument type (3A, from transaction
     C                   PARM                    SISTC
      ** Market I.D. (2A, from transaction)
     C                   PARM                    SMRKT
 
